bug.summary: SameDiff CUDA test failures (Java level memory management)
bug.description:
Many of the TF import tests when run on CUDA are giving this exception: <denchmark-code>java.lang.IllegalStateException: Attempting to release an array that was not allocated by this memory manager: id=45 </denchmark-code>
The same tests run on CPU are fine
